- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper is about training neural networks and achieving comparable accuracy to their 32-bit counterparts. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the paper is about improving the efficiency of neural networks. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions programming a binary matrix multiplication GPU kernel.
